\par\pard\plain \tx0\tx360\tx720\tx1080\tx1440\tx1800\tx2160\tx2880\tx3600\tx4320\fi360\ltrch\loch {\f2\fs24\b0\i0 <$Scr_Ps::0>Legacy Challenge Dungeons are a special type of Dungeon event, usually limited to a single participant. These events are normally focused on presenting the participant with specific types of obstacles in an effort to identify if they are worthy of inheriting a specific Legacy. Successful completion of a Legacy Challenge Dungeon usually rewards a powerful Race, Path, Class, or Profession as well as potent items intended for that Race, Path, Class or Profession. You cannot be permanently killed within any Challenge Dungeon.}
\par\plain {\f2\fs24\b0\i0  Legacy Challenge Dungeons are only found during the Tutorials offered as part of integrating a new Universe. }
